            </rs>. Aged 37. - <rs id="t18310407-56-punish324" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310407-56-punish324" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310407-56-defend547 t18310407-56-punish324"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
